Class TestJellyBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.impl.TestJellyBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BuilderData

    public class TestJellyBuilder
extends Object
implements BuilderData
    Test class for Jelly Builder. This class also implements the BuilderData interface to pass well defined test parameters to the builder object.
